categories: Category:Imperial Navy officers of the Galactic Empire

nodes.text: A human male Imperial officer served aboard the Imperial II-class Star Destroyer Eviscerator during the Galactic Civil War. The officer communicated Inferno Squad with Admiral Garrick Versio during the Battle of Endor. The officer subsequently informed Admiral Versio of the alignment of the climate disruption arrays on the planet Vardos to Admiral Garrick Versio during Operation: Cinder and contacted Agent Gideon Hask to inform him that the admiral wished to speak with him. Later, he participated in the Battle of Jakku where at the last moment he evacuated from the bridge of the Eviscerator by Versio's orders.
